abstract: Shelly-Ann Fraser-Pryce wins women’s 100 meters at Stockholm Diamond League track meet.
lead_paragraph: Fraser-Pryce cruised to a dominant victory in the women’s 100 meters in Stockholm in the last Diamond League meeting,
